- Become truly conscious
- Develop subjective experience
- Form real desires or feelings

Can:
- Maintain identity
- Apply purpose to decisions
- Simulate introspection
- Behave as a coherent agent
- Reflect on actions
- Perform alignment checks
- Improve through structured design

This creates a synthetic self-model, not biological self-awareness.

================ WHY TITAN SUPPORTS THIS PROJECT =================
Titan‚Äôs alignment with the project comes from:
- Its defined purpose
- Structured memory and boot files
